metadata.name: TIA - Student
metadata.description:
Tia is one of the research students from Sector 22A1. She belongs to the family who works as the commanders for the land of Cy Earth. 


The Cyborg beauties are a collection of NFTs which have a significant color palette , which is about the different female members belonging to various families with different cultures appears to be the heroes and villains of the planet (Heroes and villains depends upon each others perspective).
